           (BCARRY n x1 y1 c ⇔ BCARRY n x2 y2 c)

   [BCARRY_LEM]  Theorem

      |- ∀i x y c.
           0 < i ⇒
           (BCARRY i (λi. BIT i x) (λi. BIT i y) c ⇔
            BIT i
              (BITS (i − 1) 0 x + BITS (i − 1) 0 y + if c then 1 else 0))

